<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>10</hymn_number>
<title>KEIMAH KHAMHTU CH10</title>
<key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Khamhbawi dawtnak a ngan ngaingai, Lunglawmhnak hla ka sa lai, Sualnak
 in keimah tlanh awkah, Vai-lamtahnak ah thi cang.

[C1]
   Bawipa thangthatnak hlaka sa, A thi in a ka tawl cang; Vailamtah nak
   kha a in i, Ka sualnak kha a thlah cang.

[V2]
 Vancung ro kha co awk ca-ah, A tha bik bia a kan chimh, A kan dawtnak
 a ngan ca-ah, Kan sualnak kha a thlah cang.

[C2]
   Bawipa thangthatnak hlaka sa, A thi in a ka tawl cang; Vailamtah nak
   kha a in i, Ka sualnak kha a thlah cang.

[V3]
 A kan Khamhbawi a min a thang, Nifate ka thangthat lai, Ka thih tikah
 hell chung biaceih, Phakter kha a ka duh lo.

[C3]
   Bawipa thangthatnak hlaka sa, A thi in a ka tawl cang; Vailamtah nak
   kha a in i, Ka sualnak kha a thlah cang.

[V4]
 A kan Khamhbawi dawtnak a ngan, Hla tha in ka thangthat lai, Zungzal
 nunnak ram chungah khin, Amah he kan um lai ta.

[C4]
   Bawipa thangthatnak hlaka sa, A thi in a ka tawl cang; Vailamtah nak
   kha a in i, Ka sualnak kha a thlah cang.</lyrics>
</song>